= Pages

- Pages are created from .txt files in the main Dropbox folder
- These .txt files can contain any syntax (plain text, html)
- New lines of .txt are replaced with '<br/'>
- File name cannot contain space


= Menu

- Menu items are created automatically from Pages
- 'Home' as first menu item is automatically added

= Posts

- Every portfolio item (image, video) has its own post
- Categories / Directories can be nested
- Each category can have a descriptor .txt file
- Each image can have an additional descriptor file
- Lower level descriptors can inherit or overwrite previous descriptions


